Package org.apache.bcel

This package contains basic classes for the Byte Code Engineering Library and constants defined by the JVM specification.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Constants Deprecated
    (since 6.0) DO NOT USE - use Const instead
    ExceptionConstants Deprecated
    (since 6.0) DO NOT USE - use ExceptionConst instead
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Const
    Constants for the project, mostly defined in the JVM specification.
    ExceptionConst
    Exception constants.
    Repository
    The repository maintains informations about class interdependencies, e.g., whether a class is a sub-class of another.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ExceptionConst.EXCS
    Enum corresponding to the various Exception Class arrays, used by ExceptionConst.createExceptions(EXCS, Class...)

Package org.apache.bcel Description

This package contains basic classes for the Byte Code Engineering Library and constants defined by the JVM specification.
